title: FLOOR, CEIL, & ROUND for datetimes
sql:
select ceil ( 
    interval '+123-5' year(9) to month 
  ) as ymi_year_ceil,
  floor ( 
    interval '+0 12:34:56' day to second 
  ) as dsi_day_floor,
  round ( 
    to_date ( '12-APR-2023 12:34:56', 'DD-MON-YYYY HH24:MI:SS' ), 
    'hh24' 
  ) as dt_hour_round,
  round ( 
    to_timestamp ( '12-APR-2023 12:34:56', 'DD-MON-YYYY HH24:MI:SS' ), 
    'mi' 
  ) as ts_minute_round;
  
YMI_YEA DSI_DAY_FLOOR       DT_HOUR_ROUND        TS_MINUTE_ROUND     
------- ------------------- -------------------- --------------------
+124-00 +00 00:00:00.000000 12-APR-2023 13:00:00 12-APR-2023 12:35:00
